04/13/15 - "AH. SO NICE OF YOU TO JOIN ME."
04/13/15 - "MY MASTERPIECE!"
04/13/15 - "LET US BEGIN."
04/13/15 - "SO I WILL SHOW YOU WHAT I SAW."
04/13/15 - "AH YES. MOVIE MAGIC AT ITS BEST."
04/13/15 - "ALSO, LOOK CLOSELY."
04/13/15 - "ONE MORE BANNER PIECE OF SWAG IN MY POSSESSION."
04/13/15 - "HERE I AM LORDING IT OVER MY MINIONS."
04/13/15 - "WHEN SUDDENLY."
04/13/15 - "BUT THEN."
04/13/15 - "THEY ARE ALL FRISKY, AND READY TO FIGHT."
04/14/15 - "LIKE I SAID. I HAVE A SUPERIOR WEAPON."
04/14/15 - "AND RULES AND STUFF."

04/14/15 - "IT BECAME MYSTERIOUSLY INTANGIBLE."
04/14/15 - "SO IN THE BLINK OF AN EYE."
04/14/15 - "I SHOULD ALSO RELEVANTLY MENTION."
04/14/15 - "NOW IS WHEN THE PUMMELING BEGINS."
04/14/15 - "I'M MOSTLY TOYING WITH THEM THOUGH."
04/14/15 - "SO."
04/14/15 - "I'M RUINING THEM, REALLY."
04/14/15 - "IT WAS A PRETTY GOOD FIGHT BETWEEN US."
04/14/15 - "MY OVERCONFIDENCE, WAS MY ACHILLES DOWNFALL THOUGH."
04/14/15 - "AND BY UPSET."
04/15/15 - "THE HOPE... MY GOD."
04/15/15 - "WELL, MY SECOND MAYBE."
04/15/15 - "IT SEEMS THAT HOPE POWER IS OVERWHELMING."
04/15/15 - "I GET DUNKED AS FUCK."
04/15/15 - "MEANWHILE, STRIDER REGROUPS FROM HIS TROUNCING."
04/15/15 - "SO I GET UP. AND..."
04/15/15 - "SO BASICALLY."
04/15/15 - "THE SWEATY MUSCULAR GHOST APPEARS OUT OF NOWHERE."
04/15/15 - "THIS GIVES DIRK JUST THE TIME HE NEEDS."
04/15/15 - "I THINK HE THOUGHT HE COULD DESTROY MY SOUL."
04/15/15 - "AT THIS POINT."
04/15/15 - "YES, NEVER TO BE FOUND."
04/15/15 - "IT WILL BE TIME, INDEED, FOR ME TO GET..."
04/15/15 - "AND NOW, IF YOU WILL EXCUSE ME."
